=head1 DESCRIPTION

Specifies the configuration information needed to customize how
collapsed search result groups expand.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 MaxExpandedResultsPerItem => Int

The number of expanded results to show per collapsed primary document.
For instance, if you set this value to 3, then at most 3 results per
collapsed group will be displayed.


=head2 MaxResultItemsToExpand => Int

The number of collapsed search result groups to expand. If you set this
value to 10, for example, only the first 10 out of 100 result groups
will have expand functionality.



